                     <interp inst="t18440304-981-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> stealing 1 copper, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., and 5lbs. weight of lead, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18440304-name-841" type="victimName">
